The paper deals with online algorithms for assigning jobs to servers in the Cloud, which involves resource allocation and optimization. This falls under the scope of several arXiv CS sub-categories, including Distributed, Parallel, and Cluster Computing (cs.DC), Information Theory (cs.IT), Networking and Internet Architecture (cs.NI), Systems and Control (cs.SY), and Data Structures and Algorithms (cs.DS). However, since the paper focuses on the design and analysis of online algorithms, cs.DS and cs.DC are the most likely sub-categories. The other sub-categories are also relevant due to the networking and optimization aspects of the problem.
